    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="knx.00001.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1889-02-22">Feb: 22 '89<ptr target="knx.00001_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Y'r welcome letter rec'd this mn'g<ptr target="knx.00001_n2"/>&#8212;I am still here in good heart enough but
                almost entirely physically disabled&#8212;tied here to room &#38; chair&#8212;The
                news from O'C<ptr target="n2002"/> is not better&#8212;eyes given out, stomach, strength, bladder &#38;c,
                in bad way,&#8212;I expect Dr B<ptr target="n0119"/> to leave Canada next Monday for here&#8212;will send
                you a copy of the big book<ptr target="n4195"/> by express to West Park next week (or early in
                March)&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Best love to you &#38; 'Sula<ptr target="n0892"/> &#38; Julian<ptr
                        target="loc.01151_n1"/></salute>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="knx.00001.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
